                    <value>&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Hi&amp;nbsp;{{{Account.FirstName}}},&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
We are excited to be part of your journey towards optimal wellness. As you embark on this journey with 10X Health, we wanted to share some important information about the next steps in your blood test process.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Getting your blood test completed is a critical component of your personalized wellness plan, and we want to make sure that you have all the information you need to make the process as smooth and stress-free as possible.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
In preparation for your blood test, we encourage you to:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Hydrate by drinking plenty of water the day before.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Refrain from eating or drinking anything 8-12 hours prior to your scheduled blood draw.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Get a good night&amp;rsquo;s sleep to ensure optimal results.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Avoid fatty and fried foods, as well as alcohol, in the 1-2 days leading up to your blood test.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Not smoke before your blood draw.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Once we receive your results, we&amp;#39;ll&amp;nbsp; schedule a consultation with our expert clinical team to start working on your customized wellness plan as soon as possible. If you have any questions or concerns, don&amp;#39;t hesitate to reach out.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Thank you for choosing 10X Health!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
To your wellness,&lt;br /&gt;
